    "For example, Delson et al. (2022) discussed the impact of oral exams on student performance and motivation.",
    "One of the results they obtained showed that the group with the instructor increased their grade by 14%.",
    "Additionally, approximately 70% of the students who participated in the research strongly agreed or agreed that the oral exams increased their motivation to learn.",
